import React from 'react'
import { Container, Row, Col } from 'react-bootstrap'
import { FaChevronLeft } from 'react-icons/fa'

const DailyWorkout = ({dailyWorkout, closeDailyWorkout}) => {
    return (
        <Container>
        <Row>
            <Col><FaChevronLeft onClick={() => closeDailyWorkout}/></Col>
            <Col>{dailyWorkout.name}</Col>
        </Row>
        </Container>
    )
}
export default DailyWorkout
